# TJN Home

> [!INFO] Summary
> A powerful, CSV-driven browser startpage with smart search, DuckDuckGo autocomplete, and keyboard-first navigation. Zero dependencies, 200KB total bundle (99% reduction from original 20MB). Monochrome design with website favicons as the only color.

