## 🔑 Key Features

### CSV Configuration
- Easy link management without touching code
- Category organization (single chars or short codes)
- Website favicons/icons
- Quick launch functionality

### Smart Search
- DuckDuckGo-powered autocomplete
- Search history via localStorage
- Site-specific search with `:` delimiter (e.g., `g:query`)
- Path navigation with `/` delimiter
- Direct URL redirect
- Fallback to Google search

### Interactive UI
- Large clock display (12/24 hour format)
- Help menu with `?` key
- Quick launch with `!` key
- Real-time autocomplete suggestions
- Keyboard-first navigation

### Customization
- Theme toggle (light/dark/reversed)
- Search engine configuration
- Delimiter customization
- 100+ icons included

